TO: PYKE JOHNSON, JR.

CC, 1 p.





Hotel Windermere

666 West End Ave.

New York 25, NY.

March 15, 1959

Dear Mr. Johnson,

Many thanks for sending me the designs for jacket and title page of the Collected Poems.1

I like the two colored butterflies on the jacket but they have the bodies of ants, and no stylization can excuse a simple mistake. To stylize adequately one must have complete knowledge of the thing. I woul